汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据38条评论打出16%的腐烂度，平均得分仅4.3/10。网站共识写道：“《艾娃》有间谍惊悚大片的所有元素，但星光璀璨的演出阵容无法挽救沉闷、陈词滥调的故事<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ava_2020_2|title=Ava (2020)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Fandango|access-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218224555/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ava_2020_2|archive-date=2020-12-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据9条评论打出39/100的平均分，表示“普遍差评”<ref>{{cite web |title=Ava (2020) Reviews |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ava-2020 |website=Metacritic |access-date=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201024819/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ava-2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的盖·罗吉（Guy Lodge）认为影片“出人意料地展现制片人与明星阵容身为动作片英雄的能力，只不过马修·牛顿写的剧本过于轻描淡写、陈词滥调，让整个作品看起来更像中规中矩的电视剧试播集，而非星光熠熠的大片<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/ava-review-jessica-chastain-1234751125/ |title='Ava' Review: Jessica Chastain Has Killer Moves, But Can't Beat a Troubled Script |website=Variety |first=Guy |last=Lodge |date=2020-08-27 |access-date=2020-09-05 |archive-date=2020-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831065747/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/ava-review-jessica-chastain-1234751125/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。”《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》专栏作者博伊德·范·霍伊（Boyd van Hoeij）认为查斯坦再度扮演强悍角色，让观众十分信服。如果观众能整部电影看下去，多半要归功于她的明星魅力，这种力量几乎补偿了逐渐变得荒谬的剧情。马尔科维奇和法雷尔两位A咖巨星仿佛知道自己在拍B级片，非常享受这次机会<ref>{{cite web |date=2020-08-23 |first=Boyd |last=van Hoeij |title='Ava': Film Review |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ava-film-review |website=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2020-09-22 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917043244/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ava-film-review |url-status=live }}</ref>。

